page_title: 'Quickstart - Get started using Provisioned Deployments with Azure OpenAI Service'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started provisioned deployments on Azure OpenAI Service.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free- Obtained Quota for a provisioned deployment and purchased a commitment. > [!NOTE]> Provisioned Throughput Units (PTU) are different from standard quota in Azure OpenAI and are not available by default. To learn more about this offering contact your Microsoft Account Team.
